## Date filter

The filter is used to perform a date search in a [date field](docs.getvoxel.io_articles_date-field_.md) of your choice

## Options

- Label
- Description
- Key
- Data source: Requires a date field as source
- Input mode: Single date or Date range
- From label: If Date range mode
- To label: If Date range mode
- Placeholder: If Single date mode
- Comparison: If Single date mode is selected, you can choose comparisons

1\. Equals selected date

3\. Greater than selected date

3\. Less than selected date
- Icon
